1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:25,789 --> 00:01:30,030
[My Heart]

3
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,800
[Episode 15]

4
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:39,220
Baihe.

5
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:40,140
I'm home.

6
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:41,500
My lady!

7
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:42,940
My lady.

8
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:43,860
Thank goodness,

9
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,180
you're finally back.

10
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,700
Did the Empress punish you?

11
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:47,660
Did she pick on you?

12
00:01:48,259 --> 00:01:50,340
Don't worry, kind people like me are naturally blessed.

13
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:50,900
See?

14
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:52,100
I'm completely fine,

15
00:01:52,259 --> 00:01:53,060
not even a single scratch on me.

16
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:53,700
Good, good.

17
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,220
Your hands are all cold.

18
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:55,980
Come on,

19
00:01:55,980 --> 00:01:57,140
let's get you some rest inside.

20
00:01:57,540 --> 00:01:58,010
Let's go.

21
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,540
Lord Jin helped you find the fusang fruit?

22
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:05,699
He really is your lucky star.

23
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:06,980
If you ask me,

24
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:08,580
you two are a pair made in heaven,

25
00:02:08,730 --> 00:02:10,180
the legendary official pair.

26
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,660
Baihe,

27
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:14,410
what you are saying...

28
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:16,980
is exactly what I like to hear.

29
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:17,660
I like it.

30
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:20,660
Since the Crown Prince has broken off his marriage to you,

31
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,170
you and Lord Jin

32
00:02:22,170 --> 00:02:23,900
can naturally get together now.

33
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,300
Speaking of that,

34
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:27,940
I have His Highness to thank.

35
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,100
It was all thanks to him.

36
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:30,900
I have to show him my gratitude tomorrow.

37
00:02:31,010 --> 00:02:31,700
What a great friend.

38
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:32,940
Leave the gift of thanks to me!

39
00:02:35,579 --> 00:02:36,860
Lord Lu, by his level of magic,

40
00:02:36,890 --> 00:02:39,180
could definitely tell that the fusang fruit was fake.

41
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,660
But instead of asking you about it,

42
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:41,540
he simply handed it to the Empress

43
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,140
as it was.

44
00:02:48,650 --> 00:02:49,260
My lady,

45
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,460
the problem was already resolved.

46
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:53,220
Why do you still seem worried?

47
00:02:55,370 --> 00:02:58,460
Do you think this whole fusang fruit matter

48
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,380
is really as simple as it seems?

49
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:03,980
What do you mean?

50
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:05,740
I just don't understand.

51
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,460
With father's ability,

52
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:08,900
he could definitely tell that

53
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:10,540
the fusang fruit was a fake.

54
00:03:11,579 --> 00:03:12,940
And if he knew it was a fake,

55
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:15,180
why did he give the fake fruit

56
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,260
to the Empress

57
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,490
and put the whole Lu Mansion in danger?

58
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,340
It doesn't make sense.

59
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:22,100
You mean to say,

60
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:24,900
Master purposely handed the fake fruit in?

61
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:25,860
Lower your voice!

62
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,780
Master doesn't seem like that kind of person.

63
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,620
What made you think this way?

64
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:34,100
I can't make sense of it either...

65
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:36,220
It's just not possible.

66
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,660
What's not possible?

67
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:41,170
Elder sister, you're here.

68
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:41,700
Lady Yunxi.

69
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:43,780
Qingqing.

70
00:03:44,329 --> 00:03:45,980
Everything worked out this time,

71
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,540
I am so glad for you.

72
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:48,700
Thank you, sister.

73
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:52,860
But there are some details I just can't figure out.

74
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:56,380
Lord Jin said the fusang fruit was swapped for a fake one.

75
00:03:57,180 --> 00:04:00,260
Wo do you think is trying to harm us,

76
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:04,860
or harm the entire Lu Mansion?

77
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:07,180
You mean,

78
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:10,420
this matter was targetting the Lu Mansion?

79
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:16,180
Lady Yunxi, your tea.

80
00:04:20,890 --> 00:04:21,780
My deepest apologies!

81
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:22,660
Are you alright sister?

82
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:23,780
It's fine, it's fine.

83
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,130
How could you be so careless?

84
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:26,900
It's fine.

85
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,580
I was the one distracted by what you were saying.

86
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:30,900
Lady Yunxi, I'm so sorry.

87
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:32,450
No worries, at ease.

88
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:39,170
That reminds me, Qingqing,

89
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:42,020
now that your wedding with the Crown Prince has been called off,

90
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:43,700
are you upset?

91
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:46,540
His Highness is a kind and righteous man.

92
00:04:47,180 --> 00:04:49,780
But I only feel for him

93
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:51,740
as a dear friend.

94
00:04:52,659 --> 00:04:53,980
If we were really married,

95
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:56,260
I won't even know how to face him.

96
00:04:57,450 --> 00:05:00,380
So, to have the wedding called off

97
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,820
is great news to me.

98
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,500
But I think His Highness

99
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,020
harbors true feelings for you.

100
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:11,020
If you don't feel romantically for him,,

101
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:13,700
it's best to clarify things with him.

102
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,380
You're right.

103
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:18,580
I'll find a good time to tell him.

104
00:05:19,930 --> 00:05:21,060
Well then, rest soon.

105
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:22,140
I will visit again tomorrow.

106
00:05:23,060 --> 00:05:23,740
Safe trip, see you.

107
00:05:28,330 --> 00:05:28,980
Baihe,

108
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:30,340
what happened just now?

109
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:32,100
I don't know why,

110
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,700
but Lady Yunxi's hand shook a little just now.

111
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,180
That's true.

112
00:05:39,180 --> 00:05:40,930
She is usually calm and composed.

113
00:05:41,570 --> 00:05:43,500
But she did look rather distracted just now.

114
00:05:45,340 --> 00:05:46,060
Could it be

115
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:50,060
because I mentioned the fusang fruit?

116
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,020
You must have been really touched

117
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:55,580
when she ventured into the Manghuang forest to see you

118
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:56,980
despite the dangers.

119
00:05:57,620 --> 00:05:59,300
Sister, you went to the Manghuang forest?

120
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,420
Why didn't I meet you then?

121
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,740
I was worried for your safety

122
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:05,020
when you ventured into the forest alone.

123
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:06,500
So I went to visit you,

124
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,580
but I could not find you.

125
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:09,740
Perhaps, by then,

126
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:11,780
you have already entered the Youhuang grove.

127
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:15,940
That's strange.

128
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:19,500
How did you find the fusang fruit?

129
00:06:20,220 --> 00:06:21,660
I don't believe you were the one who swapped it.

130
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:24,820
Who am I?

131
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:27,300
I am the all-mighty Lord Jin!

132
00:06:27,570 --> 00:06:28,659
This was nothing.

133
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:30,340
And, let me tell you a secret.

134
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:32,700
There are more than one fusang tree

135
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,450
in the Manghuang forest.

136
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,420
There is one in the deepest part of the forest.

137
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:37,220
I just had to grab another fruit.

138
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,900
Master, due to circumstances, I need to harvest another fusang fruit

139
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:45,540
thus I write to inquire about the next fruiting bearing window.

140
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:49,740
But father knew that fusang fruit was fake.

141
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:51,460
Yet he gave it to the Empress anyway,

142
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:53,500
and even conspired together

143
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,220
to drug Qing'er with the Hehuan powder.

144
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,180
To think that for the sake of the magic power stone,

145
00:06:58,420 --> 00:06:59,820
father would use such unscrupulous means,

146
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:01,610
to the point of sacrificing

147
00:07:01,610 --> 00:07:03,020
Qing'er's happiness and reputation.

148
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:04,620
Will Master one day

149
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,500
do the same to you, my lady?

150
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:11,860
You're right.

151
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:14,460
I can't just sit and wait any longer.

152
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,300
Only I understand exactly

153
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,620
what the Crown Prince needs,

154
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:19,890
and only I am qualified to be the Crown Princess.

155
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:22,860
No matter what father decides to do with the magic power stone,

156
00:07:23,890 --> 00:07:25,620
I will not let anyone else get their hands on His Highness.

157
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:31,020
For the sake of that Lu Qingqing,

158
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:32,820
you have repeatedly disobeyed my orders.

159
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,810
Seems like you have grown up,  Mingyang,

160
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:37,780
and no longer hold any regards for me.

161
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:38,700
Mother,

162
00:07:39,140 --> 00:07:40,980
it is not virtuous to take advantage of others in trouble.

163
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,659
Have you not always taught me that

164
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:44,620
a ruler should conduct himself properly?

165
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:46,420
Using the fusang fruit as an reason to

166
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:47,460
threaten Lu Qingqing

167
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,820
to marry me as a princess,

168
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,570
is not something I can do.

169
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:52,940
Mother,

170
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:54,500
Since the fusang fruit has been retrieved,

171
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,900
let's put this matter behind us.

172
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,460
Please don't worry about it anymore.

173
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:03,620
Mother,

174
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:05,340
it will hurt my heart

175
00:08:05,660 --> 00:08:06,780
if you hurt your health over this.

176
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:09,980
I have always disapproved of Lu Qingqing.

177
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:11,900
If not for her possessing in her body

178
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:13,700
the magic power stone we need,

179
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,900
she isn't even qualified to be your concubine.

180
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:19,300
Mingyang,

181
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:21,540
why would you for the sake of this unruly brat,

182
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,860
hurt my heart again and again?

183
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,700
Lu Qingqing isn't some unruly brat.

184
00:08:27,299 --> 00:08:28,700
She is the person I like.

185
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:30,419
I love her.

186
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:31,299
Love.

187
00:08:35,059 --> 00:08:37,340
You are the future Emperor Nangong.

188
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:39,580
The Emperor of Qiyuan continent

189
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:42,740
Your love should be reserved for your throne,

190
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:44,420
for your people.

191
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:45,780
Your love

192
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,740
should be used to obtain the magic power stone,

193
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:50,140
and not be occupied by such insignificant romantic love.

194
00:08:53,980 --> 00:08:55,380
I love my people.

195
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:56,860
But I also love Lu Qingqing.

196
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:58,740
She makes me feel that

197
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:00,660
I'm not just the Crown prince.

198
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,620
I'm also a living person

199
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:04,100
with feelings and desires.

200
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:08,220
I feel anxious and lost when I can't see her.

201
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:09,900
When she is injured,

202
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:11,660
I feel more pain than her.

203
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:13,340
When she is happy,

204
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:15,260
I can't help but smile too.

205
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:16,940
And when she is sad,

206
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:19,100
I will feel even more upset than her.

207
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,300
This is my first time loving someone.

208
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,490
I want her to be happy.

209
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,420
I want to be the reason she is happy.

210
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,500
Is her happiness

211
00:09:29,730 --> 00:09:31,340
more important than your throne?

212
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,460
Mother,

213
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,140
I know the magic power stone is important.

214
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,420
And I promise you,

215
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:39,940
I will obtain it.

216
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,580
But I will my own methods

217
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,260
to retrieve it.

218
00:09:42,770 --> 00:09:44,740
I plead that mother would stop forcing Lu Qingqing.

219
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:46,620
Doing that will only push her further away.

220
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:48,340
Fine.

221
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:53,300
I know I can't convince you.

222
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:55,140
If you refuse,

223
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:57,250
it matters not what more I say.

224
00:09:58,220 --> 00:09:59,540
But you must remember.

225
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,540
You have to obtain the magic power stone.

226
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:04,140
Thank you for your understanding, mother.

227
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:06,420
I shall take my leave.

228
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:17,180
My lady,

229
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:19,900
Will you really allow His highness to marry Lu Qingqing?

230
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,300
As long as we have the magic power stone,

231
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,500
my son will inherit the throne.

232
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:26,460
As for Lu Qingqing,

233
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,460
if she could survive life in the palace or not,

234
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:32,020
that will depend on her luck.

235
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,100
Qingqing,

236
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:44,740
you didn't have to be so polite about it.

237
00:10:45,420 --> 00:10:46,420
I am more than willing

238
00:10:46,850 --> 00:10:47,620
to do anything for you.

239
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:49,100
But I feel bad.

240
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:51,100
So i thought I'd gift you something

241
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,500
to express my gratitude.

242
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:56,090
Now that the matter is resolved,

243
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,540
I hope you are happier now.

244
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:01,580
As for the rumour,

245
00:11:02,540 --> 00:11:03,860
I have already sent people to clear the air.

246
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:05,220
You have nothing to worry about.

247
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:06,810
Thank you, Your Highness.

248
00:11:07,650 --> 00:11:09,220
You are too kind to me.

249
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:10,260
To the point that

250
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:11,820
I don't know how to repay you.

251
00:11:12,220 --> 00:11:13,260
I don't need you to repay me.

252
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:15,100
As long as you're happy,

253
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:16,580
I am happy.

254
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:21,140
But you asking for nothing in return

255
00:11:21,780 --> 00:11:23,380
gives me a lot of stress.

256
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:26,100
For me you have defied the Empress

257
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:27,610
and always prioritized my needs.

258
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:29,780
To me,

259
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:32,260
your kindess is too heavy.

260
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:36,700
I have always treated you as a dear friend.

261
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:39,700
I cannot return the feelings you want.

262
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:54,770
[Lord Jin Mansion]

263
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:55,330
I'm glad this whole matter has finally concluded.

264
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:56,460
But who would have thought

265
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,540
that Lu Yunxi swapped the fusang fruit.

266
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:00,420
She has such an air of discernment on the surface,

267
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:01,580
but secretly

268
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:03,500
went as far as to frame her own sister.

269
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:05,340
The human nature is unpredictable.

270
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:07,140
Lu Yunxi.

271
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:10,020
The reason she swapped the fusang fruit

272
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:11,700
was because she has feelings for the Crown prince.

273
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,450
She did not want Lu Qinging to return to Qiyuan continent

274
00:12:14,450 --> 00:12:15,290
and become Crown princess.

275
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,700
A woman blinded by love

276
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:18,780
may be terrifying,

277
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:20,220
but she acted within boundaries,

278
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:21,500
so she is not much of a threat.

279
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,140
Then what are you worried about?

280
