557
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:32,820
not to interact with Lord Jin.

558
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,340
Why are you so rebellous?

559
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:34,820
Father,

560
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,650
Lord Jin is very nice to me.

561
00:23:37,140 --> 00:23:38,580
He even found the fusang fruit for me.

562
00:23:39,260 --> 00:23:40,820
He is not the kind of person you think he is.

563
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,820
Qing'er, you are still young.

564
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,580
A lot of things

565
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:47,860
are not exactly as they seem.

566
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,660
I am already grown up.

567
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:53,100
I can tell who is nice to me,

568
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:54,500
and who is not.

569
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:55,980
What do you mean by that?

570
00:23:58,540 --> 00:24:01,300
There is something I just couldn't understand,

571
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,700
I hope father could explain it to me.

572
00:24:03,970 --> 00:24:04,620
What is it?

573
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:09,380
No matter when the fusang fruit was swapped,

574
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:12,540
Father, you should have been able to tell with your magic capability.

575
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:16,220
But why did you hand the fake fusang fruit

576
00:24:16,540 --> 00:24:17,460
to the Empress?

577
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:22,940
I knew the fusang fruit was fake

578
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:24,020
and handed it in anyway.

579
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:25,580
That is because,

580
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:28,580
considering my status in Qiyuan Continent,

581
00:24:28,970 --> 00:24:30,540
even if it was found out,

582
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:33,620
I would at worst be guilty of oversight.

583
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:36,100
But if I cocealed it on purpose

584
00:24:36,100 --> 00:24:37,540
and was exposed by someone else,

585
00:24:37,780 --> 00:24:39,500
I would be guilty of deceit.

586
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:41,060
That is, not only for you

587
00:24:41,060 --> 00:24:43,820
but a disastrous outcome for the entire Lu Mansion.

588
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:47,340
Qing'er

589
00:24:47,980 --> 00:24:48,980
I was unfair to you,

590
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,660
you have every right to be skeptical.

591
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:55,820
I trust you,

592
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:57,660
because we are family.

593
00:24:58,740 --> 00:24:59,740
Father, you must have your reasons

594
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,900
for doing what you did.

595
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:03,540
So I don't blame you.

596
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:06,100
But regarding Lord Jin,

597
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:07,900
I'm afraid I cannot follow your orders.

598
00:25:08,580 --> 00:25:09,460
I like him.

599
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:11,300
I want to be with him all the time.

600
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:13,930
Qing'er,

601
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:17,460
I understand your feelings for Lord Jin.

602
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:20,180
But fate is something

603
00:25:20,580 --> 00:25:22,700
decided by the heavens.

604
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:25,340
The more connected you are to him,

605
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:27,500
the more you two cannot be together.

606
00:25:27,980 --> 00:25:28,740
Why not?

607
00:25:29,690 --> 00:25:30,420
Let me ask you.

608
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:32,300
Recently, has Lord Jin been hurting in the chest

609
00:25:32,660 --> 00:25:33,620
whenever

610
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:35,620
the two of you are together?

611
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:37,340
Yes.

612
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:39,570
This is because you are getting closer with him.

613
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:41,540
When you become closer with him,

614
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:42,980
you are also hurting him.

615
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:50,260
It really is because of me.

616
00:25:51,620 --> 00:25:53,420
I don't want you two to be together,

617
00:25:53,850 --> 00:25:55,980
because I don't want you to be upset in the future.

618
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:58,690
After all, Lord Jin's illness has no cure.

619
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:01,700
Qingqing,

620
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:03,730
if you love him,

621
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:05,460
you have to distance yourself from him.

622
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:07,980
Father,

623
00:26:08,420 --> 00:26:09,340
how did you know?

624
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:11,490
I happened to hear

625
00:26:11,580 --> 00:26:13,740
Lord Jin talking to his servant,

626
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:14,620
and that was how I knew.

627
00:26:14,860 --> 00:26:16,130
I would not have guessed

628
00:26:16,130 --> 00:26:17,460
that there is such a strange illness in this world.

629
00:26:21,340 --> 00:26:23,940
I see, I'm really the cause.

630
00:26:25,570 --> 00:26:28,780
All I knew at first was that my magic power improves

631
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:30,100
whenever I get close to him.

632
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:34,220
Then, he started to show signs of discomfort.

633
00:26:35,780 --> 00:26:38,060
I should have known it was because of me.

634
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:42,500
I really didn't know it would hurt him.

635
00:26:45,780 --> 00:26:46,170
Father,

636
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:48,660
do you know any way to save him?

637
00:26:48,820 --> 00:26:50,740
If I knew how to resolve it,

638
00:26:50,740 --> 00:26:53,140
I would not have stopped you two from getting together.

639
00:26:58,140 --> 00:27:01,540
So as long as I don't meet him,

640
00:27:02,620 --> 00:27:03,740
he won't hurt anymore?

641
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,700
So Qing'er,

642
00:27:08,220 --> 00:27:09,690
you have to make your decision.

643
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:29,180
Father,

644
00:27:32,810 --> 00:27:33,540
I understand.

645
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:38,380
I will avoid meeting him.

646
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:54,490
[Ciyou Kindergarten]

647
00:27:56,740 --> 00:27:57,300
Give it to me!

648
00:27:59,100 --> 00:28:00,300
Xiaoyi! I'm here!

649
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:02,540
I brought you kids lots of snacks and toys!

650
00:28:02,820 --> 00:28:03,620
Thank you big brother!

651
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:04,330
Thank you brother Sikong!

652
00:28:04,330 --> 00:28:05,980
Thank you big brother!

653
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:06,460
Here.

654
00:28:07,020 --> 00:28:07,940
Brother Sikong,

655
00:28:10,210 --> 00:28:11,890
you're a little strange lately.

656
00:28:12,730 --> 00:28:14,060
Strange in what way?

657
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:16,540
You always visit when sister Wan Qing isn't around.

658
00:28:16,540 --> 00:28:17,180
Come here.

659
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:24,020
Xiaoyi,

660
00:28:25,130 --> 00:28:28,220
I do feel a little scared to see sister Wan Qing these days.

661
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:30,700
It seems

662
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:33,100
he does mind my past.

663
00:28:34,700 --> 00:28:36,860
Why are you scared to see sister Wan Qing?

664
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:39,460
Kids won't understand.

665
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:40,980
Go enjoy the snacks.

666
00:28:41,730 --> 00:28:42,260
Go on.

667
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:07,650
[Lingqing Garden]

668
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:09,780
My lady,

669
00:29:10,090 --> 00:29:11,460
I prepared some pastries for you,

670
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:13,300
please eat something.

671
00:29:17,260 --> 00:29:17,900
My lady,

672
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,300
you promised Lord Jin yesterday

673
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:21,700
that you are going to Youhuang Hall today.

674
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:25,060
My selfishness is to be blamed.

675
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:27,180
All I thought about was stealing some magic powers.

676
00:29:27,730 --> 00:29:28,980
It never occured to me that

677
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:31,500
it would cause him so much harm.

678
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:33,260
My lady,

679
00:29:34,060 --> 00:29:35,090
I once read that

680
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:37,460
All things in this world compliment and repel each other

681
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:39,540
Though Lord Jin's illness may be rare,

682
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:42,060
it doesn't necessarily mean it's incurable.

683
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:45,780
Baihe,

684
00:29:46,140 --> 00:29:46,850
you are right!

685
00:29:47,490 --> 00:29:48,820
If it's an illness

686
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,340
there must be a way to cure it.

687
00:30:06,860 --> 00:30:08,100
For headache,

688
00:30:10,170 --> 00:30:11,220
for fever,

689
00:30:12,540 --> 00:30:13,860
for flu,

690
00:30:15,340 --> 00:30:16,380
for bone fracture...

691
00:30:17,180 --> 00:30:18,900
Why isn't there a single symptom here

692
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:20,780
that could match Nangong's symptions?

693
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:22,900
My lady,

694
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,250
be patient

695
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:25,340
and carefully search again.

696
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:29,700
Why don't you search with me?

697
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,100
I will start searching right away.

698
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:37,900
Knowledge is truly never enough when you need it.

699
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:44,820
Baihe, come here.

700
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:47,260
I just had a great idea.

701
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:51,570
My lady,

702
00:30:51,740 --> 00:30:52,580
you're so clever!

703
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:57,650
This way,

704
00:30:58,660 --> 00:30:59,180
hurry.

705
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:06,580
Baihe, where are you?

706
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:07,300
Hurry, hurry.

707
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:08,460
Please tend to my lady.

708
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:11,620
Greetings, Lady Qingqing.

709
00:31:12,060 --> 00:31:13,140
His Highness heard you were sick

710
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,620
and ordered the imperial physician here to see you.

711
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:16,700
Send my gratitude to His Highness.

712
00:31:17,940 --> 00:31:18,450
Lingyu

713
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:19,500
My lady is not feeling well,

714
00:31:19,660 --> 00:31:21,020
please wait outside.

715
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:22,650
I will inform you of any updates.

716
00:31:22,650 --> 00:31:23,100
Alright.

717
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:27,290
Imperial physician,

718
00:31:27,540 --> 00:31:28,380
please tend to my lady.

719
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:31,460
Miss,

720
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:34,260
pray tell where your discomfort is.

721
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:38,940
Recently, I caught a terrible illness.

722
00:31:41,380 --> 00:31:42,660
I felt chills all over my body,

723
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:45,100
my limbs were always cold,

724
00:31:46,580 --> 00:31:47,140
and my heart

725
00:31:47,860 --> 00:31:49,020
felt constant twisting pain.

726
00:31:49,860 --> 00:31:52,900
Do you by any chance know what illness this is?

727
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,060
Recently?

728
00:31:54,660 --> 00:31:56,300
How recent is recently?

729
00:31:57,660 --> 00:32:00,460
I was reading in the study yesterday

730
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:03,180
and I suddenly caught the illness.

731
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:06,370
It hurt so much, I could not stand straight.

732
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:09,580
Miss, is there any symptom for me to check right now?

733
00:32:10,220 --> 00:32:11,340
R-right now-

734
00:32:12,450 --> 00:32:13,180
Currently, well

735
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:15,300
there isn't any right now.

736
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:17,700
But I really feel miserable all over.

737
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:18,820
Miss,

738
00:32:19,140 --> 00:32:20,180
This illness must be vicious

739
00:32:20,180 --> 00:32:21,180
to strike so suddenly.

740
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:23,980
Please allow me to take your pulse instead.

741
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:24,940
Take my pulse?

742
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:27,660
My pulse is very weak right now,

743
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,420
you might not feel anything.

744
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:32,660
Could you make a diagnosis

745
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:33,780
based on my description instead?

746
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:36,900
In medicine, one must observe, listen, ask, and take the pulse of the patient.

747
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,420
The last step is particularly important.

748
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:40,810
If I do not read your pulse,

749
00:32:41,020 --> 00:32:42,940
how could I possibly diagnose your illness?

750
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:44,170
Lady Qingqing,

751
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:46,180
please lend me your hand.

752
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:48,620
What if-

753
00:32:50,060 --> 00:32:50,860
what if....

754
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:52,900
I... I draw it out for you?

755
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:53,820
Yes.

756
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:55,180
She will draw it for you.

757
00:32:55,530 --> 00:32:56,180
Draw?

758
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:04,260
Done. Here you go

759
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:06,020
Lady Qingqing,

760
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:08,540
your drawing is too mysterious,

761
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:09,810
my untrained eyes

762
00:33:10,180 --> 00:33:11,100
cannot understand it.

763
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:13,170
How can you not understand it?

764
00:33:13,660 --> 00:33:14,940
It's so well drawn!

765
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:16,820
Cold limbs.

766
00:33:16,900 --> 00:33:18,210
Twisting ache in the heart.

767
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:19,940
Lady Qingqing,

768
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,860
If you do not cooperate and let me take your pulse,

769
00:33:22,540 --> 00:33:23,820
there is nothing I can diagnose.

770
00:33:24,420 --> 00:33:25,540
Pulse taking is mandatary.

771
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:30,660
Here.

772
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:35,980
This will do.

773
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,100
Lady Qingqing,

774
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:49,140
There is indeed a problem with your pulse.

775
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:51,100
What problem?

776
00:33:51,410 --> 00:33:52,420
Your pulse is disordered,

777
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:54,100
indicating an irregular heartbeat,

778
00:33:54,540 --> 00:33:56,060
your heart is beating too fast.

779
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:57,180
This is precisely--

780
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,220
precisely what?

781
00:33:59,610 --> 00:34:01,780
Precisely the symptom of someone lying.

782
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:03,340
Lady Qingqing,

783
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,980
I am a busy person.

784
00:34:05,340 --> 00:34:06,460
You are in the pink of health

785
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,460
this is wasting my time.

786
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:09,380
I will take my leave.

787
00:34:10,739 --> 00:34:11,820
Imperial physician, please hold on.

788
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:13,980
Lady Qingqing,

789
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:15,820
why do you do this?

790
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:19,300
Actually, the symtoms I mentioned

791
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,060
are from my friend.

792
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:23,380
Due to his identity,

793
00:34:23,659 --> 00:34:25,420
he cannot meet you in person.

794
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:26,460
That's why,

795
00:34:27,420 --> 00:34:29,179
that's why I came up with this bad idea.

796
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:31,130
I see, please tell me more

797
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:32,780
about your friend's symptoms.

798
00:34:33,010 --> 00:34:34,420
Recently,

799
00:34:35,260 --> 00:34:36,580
whenever I get close to him,

800
00:34:37,010 --> 00:34:38,380
his heart starts to hurt,

801
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:39,860
chills start to surround him,

802
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:41,380
and his magic powers would weaken.

803
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:43,860
And everytime it happens,

804
00:34:44,130 --> 00:34:45,540
it's worse than the previous time.

805
00:34:46,020 --> 00:34:46,540
This...

806
00:34:47,690 --> 00:34:49,060
illness strikes whenever you get close to him.

807
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,290
Does he like you?

808
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,810
Like me?

809
00:34:54,020 --> 00:34:54,740
Imperial physician,

810
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,330
are you here to gossip

811
00:34:56,330 --> 00:34:57,460
or here to make a diagnosis?

812
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:59,260
For a great number of people,

813
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,300
illness stems from the heart.

814
00:35:00,700 --> 00:35:02,140
Naturally, I have to ask about it.

815
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,700
What kind of saying is that?

816
00:35:05,100 --> 00:35:06,700
If this illness stems from the heart growing fond,

817
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:10,060
then I dare say this is the rarest illness in Qiyuan Continent.

818
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:11,890
I have never heard of it,

819
00:35:12,090 --> 00:35:13,180
let alone treated it before.

820
00:35:15,180 --> 00:35:16,420
I see...

821
00:35:17,770 --> 00:35:18,940
Thank you for the troubles.

822
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:20,820
If you really care for him,

823
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:22,540
it is best to distance yourself from him.

824
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:25,380
His illness is rare and hard to comprehend.

825
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,900
As of now, you can only distance yourself

826
00:35:28,890 --> 00:35:30,100
to stop him from feeling ill.

827
00:35:32,890 --> 00:35:33,460
My lady,

828
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:35,020
His Highness is here to see you.

829
00:35:36,620 --> 00:35:37,060
Qingqing

830
00:35:37,580 --> 00:35:38,060
are you alright?

831
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:39,220
Where exactly does it hurt?

832
00:35:39,460 --> 00:35:40,700
I. I'm fine.

833
00:35:42,860 --> 00:35:43,610
I spoke to the Imperial physician.

834
00:35:44,060 --> 00:35:45,700
He said you were fine.

835
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,140
But if you were fine,

836
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,340
why did your heart hurt?

837
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,340
I couldn't stop worrying,

838
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:50,820
so I rushed over to see you.

839
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:52,580
I. I.

840
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:54,500
I am fine.

841
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,780
I was just kidding.

842
00:35:58,260 --> 00:35:58,860
As long as you're fine.

843
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:00,060
Qing'er

844
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:01,420
No matter what you do,

845
00:36:02,220 --> 00:36:02,820
I believe

846
00:36:03,770 --> 00:36:04,780
you have your reasons.

847
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,580
Is something bothering you?

848
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:12,340
If you don't mind,

849
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,580
you could always share it with me

850
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:14,820
I will bear it with you.

851
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:20,460
Recently, a friend of mine

852
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,380
is feeling unwell.

853
00:36:23,340 --> 00:36:25,700
Whenever I get close to him,

854
00:36:26,380 --> 00:36:27,500
his heart start to ache,

855
00:36:28,460 --> 00:36:30,180
chills would surround him,

856
00:36:31,090 --> 00:36:32,420
and his entire body starts to frost up.

857
00:36:33,860 --> 00:36:35,580
I don't know why it's happening.

858
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,180
I can't believe brother

859
00:36:38,860 --> 00:36:40,660
contracted such a strange illness.

860
00:36:43,580 --> 00:36:44,860
Qing'er, don't worry.

861
00:36:45,370 --> 00:36:46,700
Since this involves brother's health

862
00:36:47,020 --> 00:36:47,820
I won't ignore it.

863
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,820
I'll put extra men on the lookout

864
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:50,940
to learn more about this illness.

865
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,580
How do you know I was referring to Lord Jin?

866
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,220
You don't usually go out much,

867
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:58,740
and you don't have many people close to you.

868
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:00,090
So the identity of your friend

869
00:37:00,540 --> 00:37:01,420
can be easily deduced.

870
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:07,780
Rare illnesses tend to be old,

871
00:37:09,060 --> 00:37:11,540
perhaps there are records of it in old books.

872
00:37:12,980 --> 00:37:13,900
Speaking of old books,

873
00:37:14,740 --> 00:37:15,780
The Library Pavilion in the palace

874
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:17,660
has the largest collection of books in all of Qiyuan Continent.

875
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:19,500
Perhaps there are records of it there.

876
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:22,340
I will pay the Library Pavilion a visit

877
00:37:22,570 --> 00:37:23,460
and see if I could find anything about the illness.

878
00:37:24,060 --> 00:37:24,660
But,

879
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:26,460
it will take a while.

880
00:37:26,740 --> 00:37:28,220
Can I visit the Library Pavilion too?

881
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,260
I want to look it up, too.

882
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,460
We might be faster with two people on the job.

883
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:34,140
Well...

884
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:36,220
What's wrong?

885
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:37,580
According to regulations,

886
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:40,900
Only a descendant of the Nangong royalty

887
00:37:42,260 --> 00:37:43,220
may enter the Library Pavilion.

888
00:37:45,700 --> 00:37:47,660
I'll just find a way to sneak you in.

889
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:48,660
That's great!

890
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:52,740
Since we have to do it when no one is looking,

891
00:37:53,540 --> 00:37:55,180
night time would be a good decision.

892
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:56,900
Very well,

893
00:37:57,650 --> 00:37:58,260
in two days,

894
00:37:58,490 --> 00:38:00,060
I will use a feast as an excuse to summon you to the palace.

895
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:02,690
Then we'll find a good chance to go to the Library Pavillion.

896
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:04,740
Alright.

897
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:14,010
[Lu Mansion]

898
00:38:10,620 --> 00:38:11,220
Your Highness.

899
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:14,250
I can't believe Lord Jin would contract such a strange illness.

900
00:38:16,020 --> 00:38:17,020
This doesn't sound like an illness,

901
00:38:18,020 --> 00:38:18,780
more like some kind of poison.

902
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:23,780
Who did such a vile thing to him?

903
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,140
But if you think about it from another angle,

904
00:38:27,690 --> 00:38:29,170
If Lord Jin is in this state,

905
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,900
he won't be able to be with Lady Qingqing.

906
00:38:31,220 --> 00:38:32,620
This is a good chance for you, Your Highness.

907
00:38:33,370 --> 00:38:34,140
Do not speak such nonsense.

908
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:36,220
Romance matters aside,

909
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,700
he is above all, my brother.

910
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:39,100
If he is sick,

911
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:40,460
I will be worried as well.

912
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:41,570
Let's go,

913
00:38:42,140 --> 00:38:42,780
to Lord Jin Mansion

914
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:43,300
Understood.

915
00:38:42,990 --> 00:38:45,050
[Lord Jin Mansion]

916
00:38:58,660 --> 00:38:59,300
Brother,

917
00:39:00,460 --> 00:39:01,940
perhaps you should stop seeing Qingqing from now on.

918
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:04,820
What do you mean.

919
00:39:05,300 --> 00:39:06,220
Why are you telling me this.

920
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:06,980
For your own good,

921
00:39:07,940 --> 00:39:08,780
and for her own good.

922
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:10,700
The two of you are not meant to work out.

923
00:39:12,780 --> 00:39:13,260
Mingyang,

924
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:16,180
she is no longer your Crown Princess-to-be.

925
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:17,420
But brother,

926
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:19,140
you knew that just being with her

927
00:39:19,140 --> 00:39:19,980
will result in unbearable heartache.

928
00:39:20,140 --> 00:39:21,660
If this goes on, you will die.

929
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:22,420
How did you know?

930
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:25,100
Qingqing told me.

931
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:26,730
I visted her just now.

932
00:39:27,570 --> 00:39:28,860
She is still in Qiyuan continent?

933
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:29,860
What did she tell you?

934
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:31,770
Brother.

935
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:33,860
Perhaps it is fate toying with us.

936
00:39:34,580 --> 00:39:36,180
The two of you are not meant to work out.

937
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:37,860
You're just going to hurt each other like this,

938
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:38,860
stop while you still can.

939
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:39,860
I don't want

940
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,140
either of you to be hurt.

941
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:42,540
I'm going to see her now.

942
00:39:42,980 --> 00:39:44,100
She may not see you recently.

943
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,690
You should take good care of your health in the meanwhile.

944
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:53,020
I will also send people out to seek a solution.

945
00:39:53,660 --> 00:39:54,580
Hope it will be of help.
